beer.beer_name: Idaho 7 Single Hop Triple Oat Cream IPA
beer.beer_description: For GABS 2021, our fans have been asking us to have a crack at the Oat Cream IPA style. We thought we would brew a Single hop TIPA featuring the new Idaho 7 hop. Packed full of tangerine and tropical flavours and aromas, with the creaminess of the oats and lactose.
